05-25T04:01:38.000Z","msg":"技術俾人偷曬<br />\n經濟俾人入侵<br />\n屋企俾難民住曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a6768e15b45c75ddc258cc6dfd165414d53d71","tid":677130,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac7d143d4f7598b3281c4bc81eb156b6bd33540","tid":677130,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d45c81e908251cf952526b551051bf073bfd859f","tid":677130,"uid":38671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"美國國策正式轉向，侵連唔連到任都分別不大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"好多人仲以為關侵事，其實民主黨都暗中改變咗對華態度"},{"pid":"05190c6ba515b03483c0597cc70b65ffa385c660","tid":677130,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ac7d143d4f7598b3281c4bc81eb156b6bd33540","tid":677130,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d45c81e908251cf952526b551051bf073bfd859f","tid":677130,"uid":38671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"美國國策正式轉向，侵連唔連到任都分別不大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"好多人仲以為關侵事，其實民主黨都暗中改變咗對華態度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:11:14.000Z","msg":"係侵侵自己撩起 支國威脅論嘅火頭<br />\n本身覺得係談判籌碼<br />\n搞搞吓分分鐘變成國策方針"},{"pid":"40196a47d097a22fb99fcdc55b7294194daf8558","tid":677130,"uid":116443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:42:19.000Z","msg":"侵侵正式將中俄朝列為邪惡軸心國，黎緊又有好多場戲睇"},{"pid":"2d527a5012e5ba316ddf56e58a3b87d62699afc7","tid":677130,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"仲支援台灣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦眾議院今天上午以351票贊成、66票反對，通過2019財政年度國防授權法（HR 5515）草案。該法案要求提升台灣防衛能力，美方並派遣軍事高層訪台，落實台美軍事高層交流。<br />\n<br />\n根據眾院軍委會本月7日公佈的2019DNAA草案提出，美國應協助台灣提升防衛能力，評估台灣軍力，支持對台軍售，以期做為抗衡中國大陸的戰略之一。草案第1262條並寫明，美國國會意見指出，根據台灣旅行法，美國國防部應派遣軍種部長或參謀首長聯席會議成員到台灣，進行高階官員互訪。<br />\n<br />\n此外，草案第1253條要求，美國國防部長應與台灣對等部門諮商，全面評估台灣軍力，包括台灣後備軍力在內，就提升台灣自衛能力提出建議，並要求在法案生效12個月內，國防部長應與國務卿諮商，向相關委員會提交報告，說明評估結果、建議清單與計劃採取的方案。2018財政年國防授權法也提出此一要求。<br />\n<br />\n國防授權法草案在經眾議院表決通過後，參議院軍事委員會將對此進行辯論，並討論出參議院版本後送參議院院會表決。參議院表決通過後，若與眾議院版本不同，參眾兩院還將協商討論最後版本，並經兩院表決後，才會送交美國總統簽署生效。<br />\n<br />\n(中時 )<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180525001073-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180525001073-260408&d=IzNnsw2NHj6Y0EKC5Yge5dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=84b276fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180525001073-260408</a>"},{"pid":"d82f689fac0b351ee2f50b5907f0c0b9c119f291","tid":677130,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"凌遲支俄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39bb3fecfa2814725d848497fb3b3a58663d53ce","tid":677130,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"def3aa7b7b41e0f61f78a29000b5e745abec6402","tid":677130,"uid":42921,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"美國啲歐洲盟友仲懵盛盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"人地freeride美軍<br />\n不知幾醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81eeed65e56bc89ec3af1a70ff471a3c38ad7445","tid":677130,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"等埋侵侵簽署就成法律？"},{"pid":"3dc11d68cdba8b21cf4b69cf74134e6e93f99248","tid":677130,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9